    <summary>View Oracle .dmp files (EXP &amp; EXPDP) without Oracle — free for personal use</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[## Open DUMP Viewer for Oracle database

View and export Oracle database dump files (.dmp) **without Oracle Database or Client**.

### Features

- **No Oracle required** — parse EXP (Oracle 7–11g) and EXPDP / Data Pump (Oracle 10g–23ai) files directly
- **Schema tree** — hierarchical schema → table browsing
- **Data preview** — paginated viewing for tables with millions of rows
- **Advanced search** — 12 operator types with AND/OR compound conditions
- **Export** — CSV, SQL (Oracle/PostgreSQL/MySQL/SQL Server), Excel, Access, ODBC, SQL Server direct import
- **LOB extraction** — extract BLOB/CLOB data as individual files
- **10 languages** — Japanese, English, Chinese, Korean, German, French, Spanish, Italian, Russian, Portuguese
- **Partition support** — view partitioned table structures and individual partition data

### Licensing

- **Free** for personal and educational use (all features included)
- Professional: ¥4,900/year ($32) — freelancers & sole proprietors
- Business: ¥9,800/year ($65) — companies & commercial use

Get your license at [https://www.odv.dev/](https://www.odv.dev/)

### Notes

- This package installs the EXE installer which includes shortcuts and .dmp file association
- .NET runtime is bundled — no additional runtime installation needed
]]></description>
